386→                        <div id="content">Let $B_1$ be the Boolean algebra of sets of integers modulo sets of density $0$ (that is, in which two sets are equivalent if and only if they differ by a set of density $0$) and let $B_2$ be the Boolean algebra of sets modulo sets of logarithmic density $0$.<br><br>Prove that $B_1$ and $B_2$ are not isomorphic.</div>
